{"tid":266283,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）想搵一套關於蛇既電影","createTime":"2017-06-01T10:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T20:24:35.000Z","uid":18863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33b71e00ecfa57dd9ebf75d256a867c45c7a176e","tid":266283,"uid":18863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"好耐之前睇過 喺歐美片黎<br />\n講有班人佢地困住咗 個地方有好多蛇<br />\n好似係坐船 然後佢地係船上拎返啲物資黎用<br />\n有一幕喺夜晚 班人要由左邊去右邊<br />\n但中間夾住條河/湖 水入面有好多蛇<br />\n咁佢地就決定整纜索fing過去<br />\n好似咁樣<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/01/184309_62cbe85bfc74d02ac717ee12ccc0cb3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F01%2F184309_62cbe85bfc74d02ac717ee12ccc0cb3a.jpg&h=aa4a2c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外有一幕喺主角行入一間當地酒吧<br />\n之後見到酒吧牆上釘咗個新聞<br />\n話有人擸蛇既新聞 之後斷腳定死咗（唔太清楚）<br />\n依幕唔記得喺咪同一套電影<br />\n有無人知喺咩電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"eac2f3afacbf59ae02d5f0cca020abe7087fc475","tid":266283,"uid":18863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:02:12.000Z","msg":"輕推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2090c33ad07faa5c2fc633a6dbcb3e0438d578","tid":266283,"uid":99212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"無蟒之災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34899081eb8046b44a0c2aafa7a5ec5513cd7dbc","tid":266283,"uid":99212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:16:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無蟒之災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係，唔敢肯定，好細個睇過"},{"pid":"0838aff98140ca67dc83beebdb740b59cea70ca6","tid":266283,"uid":36451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:16:51.000Z","msg":"飛機上有蛇"},{"pid":"6f1bd796d1bb2dcd6688f88fb8365443fed72bf6","tid":266283,"uid":18863,